            <div type="a">
                <column>7</column>
                <head>Truthful and Eloquent Extras</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p>"Not less identified with the growth of our empire is the name and fame of
                        the Democratic party."</p>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Article applauds Democratic values and the strength of the Democracy from
                    Jackson's time forward.</summary>
            </div>
