                <head>The Election--Positively for the Last Time</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p>"...we call upon our Democratic brethren throughout of Virginia and the South
                        to unite with us in sincere prayer to the Almighty, that he may never elate
                        out hearts by a 'Whig victory.'"</p>
                </transcript>
