                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Article mocks an attached article that says all the country's conservative
                    elements are uniting against the Democracy, and assures readers that the
                    Democracy is the party of conservatives.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
