            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>Fourth of July and Ladies' Fair</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p>The ladies of the Methodist E. Church will hold their annual Fair at Union Hall, in Staunton, on 
                        the 4th and 5th of July.--An unusual effort will be made by the ladies on this occasion, as the 
                        proceeds of the Fair, Supper, &amp;c;, will be strictly appropriated to aid us in the erection of a 
                        new Methodist E. Church in Staunton. Our fellow-citizens and visiting friends are most 
                        respectfully invited to give the ladies their presence and patronage.
                    </p>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The ladies of the Methodist E. Church will hold a fair on the 4th and 5th
                    of July to raise money for the construction of a new church.</summary>
                <note>aubrowser/rvjune59.html#6.11b</note>
            </div>
